skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guess my word
des:
Guess a word and Alexa will tell you if her word comes alphabetically before or after your guess! She will also tell you how many times you've played so far and how many guesses you took to get to the right word. 

During your play, if you would like to give up, you can just say "I give up" or "I don't know" and Alexa will tell you what her word was!

If you've changed your wake-word from "Alexa" to "Echo", "Amazon", or "Computer" then use that instead of "Alexa".

Go ahead and start guessing! Good luck!!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
